# Build outputs & caches (large, high-churn — keep out of Cursor context)
**/build/
**/.gradle/
**/.kotlin/
**/captures/
**/.cxx/
**/.externalNativeBuild/
**/intermediates/
**/generated/
**/tmp/
**/out/

# Local SDK / tooling (often huge)
**/.android-sdk/
**/android-sdk/
**/.emulator/

# IDE & OS
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets & machine-local
**/local.properties

# Python / automation state
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/automation/.state/

# Aider / local agent artifacts
**/.aider*

# Optional: shrink noise from dependency trees if ever added
**/node_modules/
